type.how2prepare:
in a cocktail shaker with ice, add one shot of vodka, one shot of kahlua and double espresso and shake it for 20 seconds;
pour the mix on the martini glass;
garnish with a couple of coffee beans on top and baileys to extra flavour.

type.ingredients:
Vodka;
Cointreau;
Lime;
Sugar syrup;
Cranberry juice;

type.how2prepare:
in a cocktail shaker with ice, add one shot of vodka, half shot of cointreau, one cap of sugar syrup, squeeze half lime and top up with cranberry juice and shake it for 20 seconds;
pour the mix on the martini glass;
garnish with a slice of lime.

