type.how2prepare:
In the cocktail shaker with ice add one shot of bourbon, one cap of sugar syrup, 2 dashes of angostura bitters, one egg white, juice from one squeezed lemon and shake it;
pour the mix into the whisky glass and add a few cubes of ice;
garnish with wedge of lemon.
